race.comment: MAJESTIC LOUVRE (2) defied market expectations when a runner-up in town last time out and looks to be improving with racing. Will find this assignment easier and looms as the main danger. WORLDY SPIRIT (7) returned in good order with a second at Gatton and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Top-three aspirations. NEWELL BEACH (3) will be rock-hard fit for this and may earn some minor money along with CANCELLED (11) who will be fitter for recent racing.
